A woman in athletic wear is standing on a paved path with a body of water and greenery in the background. She is holding a bottle of what appears to be a sports drink. Her shirt says "RUN AWAY CLUB".

The image shows a person in cycling gear standing next to a Giant road bike. The post includes stats from a morning ride: 116.6 km, 403 m elevation gain, and a time of 4 hours and 58 minutes. The location appears to be in Phuket, as indicated by the hashtag #zcoachingphuket.

The image shows a person in running attire standing on a road next to a body of water and hills. The person is holding a small item in their hand, possibly an energy gel or snack. The caption mentions "Interval running Day Wednesday Dam!"

The image shows a screenshot of an Instagram post by ninger_runnerr. The post features a photo of a beach with the ocean and trees in the background. The caption describes an open water swim, mentioning distance, time, and pace. The caption also mentions training, tonsillitis, and swimming with a buddy named Emma.

The image shows a lantern attached to a white wall, with greenery and yellow flowers in the background. The post is captioned "Raining in summer time" and tagged #soontreehouse. The location is Phuket, Thailand.
